[
  {
    "text": "Greg Bradley: Hello, App Store developers! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "I’m Greg from the App Store Review team.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our goal is to help developers find success on the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're an international team with reviewers on three continents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "fluent in over 80 languages, working around the clock ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "to give you feedback on your apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today I’m going to share tips from our team ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you prepare your apps for review ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "and get ahead of some of the common issues we see.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "The three tips we have for you today will help you avoid issues ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "that we find on 30 percent of rejected submissions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "These issues are as common as they are preventable.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "Implementing these tips before you submit your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "will make your submission ready for your customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "and also ready for us to conduct our review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "To help visualize that, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "we’ll describe the journey of two apps: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "one that implements all of these tips, and one that doesn't.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll call it, \"A Tale of Two Apps.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "And we’ll touch on some additional resources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can check out to help you before, during, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "and after you submit your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our three submission tips are: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "test thoroughly so that your app is ready for your customers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "tell us more about the unique experience your app provides, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provide access, setting us up to do a complete review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's start with testing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=79"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your app may have a great concept, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "but bugs and crashes can ruin the experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "So when we find a major bug, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "or your app crashes during our review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "we’ll let you know and do our best to help you fix the issue.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll share the steps to reproduce these issues, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "and for crashes, provide crash logs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "We review all apps on physical devices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "not on a simulator, to mirror actual, real-world conditions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "The issues we see will also impact everyone using your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we want to help you prevent that.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "The best time to fix a bug or crash, though, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "is before you submit.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "At App Review, we review apps the way a user would use them, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "not necessarily in the way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "that a proper QA team would QA them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "A great tool to help you do quality assurance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "and beta testing on real, physical devices is TestFlight.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "TestFlight makes it easier to resolve issues in beta ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "before you hit production.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can upload beta builds right in App Store Connect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "and distribute to internal testers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your Apple Developer Program account.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also share your beta app to users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "with iOS, iPadOS, macOS, and tvOS devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "by inviting them via email or by sharing a public link.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "TestFlight builds are also reviewed by App Store Review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "We may reject a TestFlight submission if it has issues ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "that would prevent beta testing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "or has content that would never be on the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our TestFlight reviews exist ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you resolve App Store Review guideline issues ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "before the app is submitted to the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it’s also accessed with your developer account, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "you could start testing today! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=177"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app is live on the store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you’re submitting a critical update to fix some issues, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "we're happy to work with you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get that update to your customers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "This includes what we call \"bug fix submissions.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "If we find an issue with your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "during our review of an update, we'll let you know ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ask if you'd like to resolve the issue ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=195"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the next submission.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "If so, we'll approve the update.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a simple process and we'll let you know if you're eligible ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "in our message to you in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep in mind though, apps with legal, trust, or safety concerns ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "are not eligible for this process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let’s imagine these types of preparations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the context of two apps being submitted.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "We’ll call them Turtlr and R-bit.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "For one of these apps, the developer took the time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "to go through an industry-standard QA process, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "while the other cut some corners ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "and sped past the testing phase right into submission.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you’re familiar with heavy-handed idioms, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can probably guess which one is which! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "Turtlr had a full round of QA using TestFlight, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "after which the developer was fairly certain ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "that it was bug free, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it runs really nicely on all of the tested devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "R-bit didn't use TestFlight ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "and did a quick, but noncomprehensive QA.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "There were a couple of lingering bugs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "and sometimes it crashes when we try to sign in.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s move on to our second tip.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell us more about your app when you submit! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "You’ve worked tirelessly to make an excellent app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we’d be happy to read about your app’s concepts and features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your own words.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "We encourage you to provide any information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the App Review Information section ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the app version page in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you submitting a new app for the first time? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell us about your app's concept, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to enable key features, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "and even describe the target audience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "you designed your app for.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you submitting a big update? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell us about what’s changed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "and where to locate significant new content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also keep in mind that as apps change, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "we may ask you questions you answered ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "on previous submissions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is to make sure our understanding of your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "keeps pace with all the improvements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "and new features added over time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another thing to keep in mind is that some apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "may require additional documentation, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as from a regulatory agency, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "or to demonstrate authorization to use protected content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, if you’ve worked hard ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "to secure regulatory approval for an app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "that syncs with medical hardware, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can attach the documentation when you first submit your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you’re wondering whether or not you should ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "submit documentation, it never hurts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide us with more information about your app -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "especially if you’re operating in a highly regulated industry.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "To learn more about apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "that may require additional documents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "see guidelines 1.3, 1.4, 4.1, 5, and 5.2.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember, it’s up to you to comply with local laws ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "wherever your app is available.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=353"
  },
  {
    "text": "If we need additional information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "about any of the features or functionality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll let you know via an Information Needed message.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "But if you can anticipate the type of questions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "that a person using your app might have, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "this information could help streamline your app’s review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s check in on our slightly cliche metaphor real quick.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "Turtlr put the time into fully describing the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as helping us understand who the app is for, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "not only in the app description, but in the notes for App Review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, they were not sure if we needed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "documentation for regulatory clearance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "but they’ve gone ahead and submitted that anyway.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "R-bit’s plan for marketing their app is to be mysterious ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create some buzz, but perhaps too mysterious ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "because when they submitted the app for review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "there’s not a lot of information about what the app is or does.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "We’ll have to spend some time figuring that out.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "Even when one launches the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "it’s got a bit of a learning curve.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=409"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, let’s move on to our third tip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "and see how that can help streamline a submission! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "We review the entire app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "so if there are account-based features, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "we need to review the app experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "both with and without an account.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "Two ways to accomplish this are either with a demo account, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "or by creating a demo mode.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s talk about demo accounts first.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "Provide us with up-to-date login credentials ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a demo account in App Store Connect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that we can easily access any account-based experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ensuring the account is up to date is an important step ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "because while we may create a new account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "to review the sign up flow, you know best ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "the experience that you want users with accounts to have.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app doesn't have an account-creation feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "it’s even more important ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "to provide this up-to-date login information.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, if it makes sense to do so based on your app’s concept, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "fully featured demo accounts populated with relevant content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=462"
  },
  {
    "text": "can help show us your app in its best light.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, if you’re creating a social media platform, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can populate the demo account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "with content that really shows off the services ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "and experiences your app provides.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "For apps that handle sensitive user information, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "or operate in highly regulated industries ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "with restrictions on creating new accounts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "consider building in a demonstration mode, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "like one your QA or marketing teams ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "may already be using.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "Demonstration modes exhibit your app’s full features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "and functionality to us, while using stand-in data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "We understand that you may be working with data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "that simply cannot be shared externally, even with Apple.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "With a demonstration mode, you can help us understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=504"
  },
  {
    "text": "the entire user experience from beginning to end ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "without compromising any sensitive user information.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s compare this demo account preparation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=513"
  },
  {
    "text": "using our thinly veiled rabbit-versus-turtle analogy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "Turtlr’s account was up to date and working.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "This might seem like an obvious first step ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "but invalid or expired account credentials ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "are something we observe rather frequently! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "The account provided was populated and looked lived in, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "as if we were taking a look at the existing account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "of someone who uses the app daily.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "This created a natural user experience for us.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "It’s as if we’d been using the app forever ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "even though this is the first time we launched it! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "R-bit’s demo account, however, was expired.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well that’s that; we’ll try creating our own if we can, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "otherwise, we'll have to ask for some updated credentials.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "Getting close to the finish line here.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "Will Turtlr or R-bit cross it first? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s put all of that together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "and see the conclusion of our Tale of Two Apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=562"
  },
  {
    "text": "Turtlr followed all of these tips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "and did a couple of relatively simple things.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "They QA’d their app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=570"
  },
  {
    "text": "they provided some detailed info, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "and they made sure the demo account existed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "and was functional.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "R-bit did a little bit of testing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "but not enough to catch all of the issues.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "They didn't give us or their prospective audience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "much guidance on how to use the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the demo account had expired some time before submitting.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "With Turtlr, the time spent preparing the app for submission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "ended up saving them time in the end.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=596"
  },
  {
    "text": "They submitted the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=598"
  },
  {
    "text": "and after doing a thorough review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "we approved their submission ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "since there were no other issues.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "R-bit, however, ran into a couple of obstacles.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=605"
  },
  {
    "text": "Without a working demo account, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=608"
  },
  {
    "text": "and having a handful of usability issues ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "including some bugs and concept clarity concerns, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will take more time for the app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=615"
  },
  {
    "text": "to be ready for the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "Both apps did get approved, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "but by more thoroughly preparing the app for submission, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "our turtle friend here -- much like the turtle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may have heard about in a story or two -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=625"
  },
  {
    "text": "ends up taking the win at the end.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=628"
  },
  {
    "text": "What does that time look like in the real world? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=631"
  },
  {
    "text": "We complete our review in less than 24 hours ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "for 90 percent of apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "Reject or approve, you’ll typically get an answer from us ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=638"
  },
  {
    "text": "in about a day.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means that if there are no issues with submission, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=643"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's likely your app will be reviewed and approved ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=646"
  },
  {
    "text": "in under 24 hours.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "If there are some things to fix, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll also likely know in under 24 hours.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=653"
  },
  {
    "text": "But, if it takes multiple submissions to solve the issue, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "it may take a few days for your app to be ready for approval.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "We understand the difference between one day and a few days ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=662"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be significant in the world of apps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "so we are happy to provide these tips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=668"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help your app be ready for approval ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "without needing multiple submissions and reviews.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "We’ll close out by pointing you to some additional resources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep in mind as you submit apps to the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "The first resource is the person reviewing your app! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=683"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you’ve heard from App Store Review ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "about an issue with your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=687"
  },
  {
    "text": "but you don’t understand our requirements, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=689"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can reply to our message right in App Store Connect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "and let us know.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "We’re happy to explain the issue ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=694"
  },
  {
    "text": "and help you understand our guidelines.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you’re facing extenuating circumstances, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=699"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as submitting an update with a critical bug fix ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "or a time-sensitive event, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=703"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may request an expedited review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "Be sure to let us know your circumstances ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=710"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we’ll do our best to support you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=712"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you think we’ve misunderstood your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=715"
  },
  {
    "text": "and disagree with the outcome of our review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=716"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can file an appeal with the App Review Board.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "Be sure to provide specific reasons ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=723"
  },
  {
    "text": "why you believe your app follows our guidelines ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help the App Review Board consider your case.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=726"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can find links to the forms for requesting an expedite ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=730"
  },
  {
    "text": "or filing an appeal on the App Review page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Apple Developer website.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=735"
  },
  {
    "text": "There you can also find more tips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=738"
  },
  {
    "text": "for preparing your app for review ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=739"
  },
  {
    "text": "and other common issues to look out for.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=741"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching our video.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-10885/?time=744"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're always excited to see the next big thing ",
